'''Greg Lane''' is a New Zealand stuntman. He played various [[orcs]] and [[Uruk-Hai]] (including the torch-bearer at [[Battle of the Hornburg|Helm's Deep]]), and was the stunt double of [[Saruman]] and [[Isildur]].
